CORE COMMAND SET.
 See manual for full listing.
 v[port]=[value]   	Set voltage (V)
 i[port]=[value]   	Set current (mA)
 v[port]?          	Query voltage
 i[port]?          	Query current
 vipall?           	Query all values
 vmax[port]=[value]	Set voltage limit (V)
 imax[port]=[value]	Set current limit (mA)

ERROR CODES.
 00   		Unknown error
 01   		Overvoltage
 02   		Overcurrent
 03   		Power error
 04   		Calibration error
 10   		Unrecognised command
 11   		Unrecognised parameter
 12   		Unrecognised port
 13   		Operation forbidden
 14:00		Instruction buffer overflow
 14:01		Single instruction overflow
 15:X0		Serial overflow detected
 15:X1		Serial framing error detected
 16   		Internal software error
